# This document holds instructions for downloading and creating OMNIGLOT sample dataset
This dataset **must** be used in accordance to its own license and terms
information taken from: https://github.com/brendenlake/omniglot
original paper: http://science.sciencemag.org/content/350/6266/1332

## General Information
This dataset contains 1623 different handwritten characters from 50 different alphabets.
Each of the 1623 characters was drawn online via Amazon's Mechanical Turk by 20 different people

## Download
1. Go to: https://github.com/brendenlake/omniglot/tree/master/python
2. Download any one of the zip files

## Folder Structure Preparation
1. Extract the zip files and pass the parent directory when running the algorithm